::Rodimus Prime::

The explosian had trashed quite a few of the CR chambers, and caused a
loss of power to his. He woke up, fully healed, and got out of the
chamber. It may of lost power, but it was still in one piece, as was he.
He started to make his way outside, climbing through the ruble, looking
for bots who needed help.
